name: Circle 9
description:
You awaken at Circle 9, the most popular club in town, with no memory of how you got here. Or why time seems to have stopped.

Explore the club at different points in time and listen in on past conversations to try and figure out what happened.

Featuring the voice talents of:

  • Ariana Mertz
  • Brandon Nguyen
  • Rami Shreim
  • Ali Abdul Rahman
  • Dorian Cromartie
  • Lyndon de la Torre
  • Brian Dizon
  • Riley Park
  • Kiara Mendaros
  • James Bates
  • Nathan Graves
  • Andy Nilbog
  • Rhys Weathers
  • The 8552nd Epic Man
  • Nathan Hansen
  • Anthony Cano

Music by:

  • Christian DeTamble - http://therefactory.bplaced.net
  • Perry Butler AKA iosys/hectavex - opengameart.org
  • Emma_MA - opengameart.org

Made for the VGDC Spring Jam 2021. The theme was "iteration."
